        "when": "2021-01",
        "text": "My fiancé and I planned a last minute work-vacation shortly after getting engaged, and wanted to capture some engagement photos while we were  in Telluride. I found Wren through Google and she was so prompt in getting back to me. We were able to capture photos in a number of different locations, and her turnaround was so fast. Her work is beautiful; I'm so glad we were able to find her. I'd definitely recommend her, and if we're ever back in town and want family pictures we'll absolutely be reaching out to her."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2024-01",
        "text": "Wren is so awesome and helpful. She created beautiful fall Senior pictures for my daughter that totally met our desires.  She included different settings, mountains, the valley and outdoor portraits that were beautiful with the fall colors. It was important to us to capture the feel of the area, as my daughter had grown up in Telluride.\nWe were very happy with the quality and interaction with Wren, she was thorough and creative and we received many options to work with. Thank You Wren!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2021-08",
        "text": "Our family of 6 headed to Telluride for a last week vacation~ I think there is so much value in hiring photographers!! Especially when you travel, totally worth every penny!! Wren did a fantastic job! I cannot express enough how thankful I am for her work she did for us. First of all, she responded right away and we were able to schedule a shoot. There was smoke from the Cali fires, so she was gracious and flexible to fit us in on our last night there. Our pictures were edited and delivered quick and look amazing!! If you are planning to be in Telluride, hire Wren to take your pictures! She does everything from elopements, family, engagements, etc! She is darling, easy to talk to, professional and truly talented!"
      },
      {
